title: Mantronix - In Full Effect (192kbps MP3)
description:
Mantronix&#039;s 1988 Capitol Records debut. This CD has the distinction of being the first ever album mastered 100% digitally from DAT. Mantronix were always ahead of their time and In Full Effect was an underrated and under-appreciated Old School Hip-Hop gem.

All tracks are encoded at 192kbps, ripped directly from the original CD.
